OL,3,CMost hospitality businesses operating
OL,4,Cat under 80% of capacity
OL,6,FMost hospitality establishments in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland are operating at
OL,8,Funder 80% of capacity due to rising
OL,9,Fcosts, a survey has found.
OL,11,FIt found that hospitality businesses
OL,12,Fhave had to dramatically cut their
OL,13,Fworkforce, with 87% of respondents
OL,14,Foperating below 90% of required
OL,15,Fcapacity, with the majority (55%)
OL,16,Foperating below 80% capacity.
