OL,3,CMost hospitality businesses operating
OL,4,Cat under 80% of capacity
OL,6,FIt also found that 72% of respondents
OL,7,Fhave less than six months of cash
OL,8,Freserves, with over one in five (21%)
OL,9,Fhaving no cash reserves at all, and
OL,10,Fthat as a direct result of April cost
OL,11,Fincreases, 68% have increased prices
OL,12,Fand half (50%) have cut staff numbers.
OL,14,FMembers of Hospitality Ulster, the
OL,15,FBritish Institute of Innkeeping (BII),
OL,16,Fthe British Beer & Pub Association
OL,17,F(BBPA), and UK Hospitality were
OL,18,Fsurveyed after 84,000 hospitality jobs
OL,19,Fwere lost across the UK since the
OL,20,FBudget.
