OL,6,FHospitality businesses are calling for
OL,7,Fa reduction in VAT, urgent delivery of
OL,8,Fmeaningful lower business rates
OL,9,Fmultipliers and amendment of April's
OL,10,Fchanges to Employer National Insurance
OL,11,Fcontributions.
OL,13,FThey are also calling for an alignment
OL,14,Fof business/non-domestic rates in
OL,15,Fdevolved nations to match incoming
OL,16,Freforms in England.
OL,18,FColin Neill, chief executive of
OL,19,FHospitality Ulster, said businesses
OL,20,Fare being squeezed.
