OL,3,CMost hospitality businesses operating
OL,4,Cat under 80% of capacity
OL,6,F"This shocking data reinforces the
OL,7,Furgent need for the UK Government and
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland Executive to
OL,9,Frecognise the incredible pressure
OL,10,Fhospitality businesses have been put
OL,11,Funder, particularly since April, and
OL,12,Fillustrates why it should come forward
OL,13,Fwith measures to support this vital
OL,14,Fsector at the Budget," he said.
OL,16,F"Unsustainable tax increases are
OL,17,Fsqueezing businesses, stifling growth
OL,18,Fand investment, and threatening local
OL,19,Femployment, especially for young
OL,20,Fpeople.
