OL,6,F"It is forcing businesses across the
OL,7,Fsector to make impossible decisions to
OL,8,Fcut jobs, put up prices, reduce
OL,9,Fopening hours and sadly limit the
OL,10,Fsupport they desperately want to give
OL,11,Ftheir communities.
OL,13,F"Hospitality is united in which
OL,14,Fmeasures will reverse this trend and
OL,15,Fdrive growth, a reduction in VAT for
OL,16,Fhospitality, changes to employer NICs
OL,17,Fand the delivery of a fair rating
OL,18,Fsystem through the review currently
OL,19,Funderway at the Department of Finance.
